QuestData.Title: A Bittersweet Prize
QuestData.Description:
I... I don't know what to say.
All that is left is to return Willo... the vessel... to Polemarch Adrestes in Bastion. This sacrifice must not be in vain.
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver the Vessel of Ardenweald to Polemarch Adrestes at Elysian Hold in Bastion.
